&lt;h3&gt;Who you are&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Metropolis is seeking a commercially-minded, externally-facing Manager of Future Mobility to own site selection and activation for a portfolio of Future Mobility partner deployments. In this role, you will activate our 4,500+ location portfolio to meet the operational needs of autonomous vehicle hubs, drone delivery nests, robot delivery stations, and eVTOL vertiports. Sitting at the intersection of real estate, operations, and business development, you will serve as the connective tissue between our partners, asset owners, and internal teams to support our most ambitious partnerships and drive significant long-term growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead site assessment and selection across the 4,500+ location portfolio for AV, drone delivery, robot delivery, and eVTOL partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Project-manage site retrofits to enable Future Mobility operations by working cross-functionally with real estate, procurement, and operations teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary liaison between Future Mobility partners, asset owners, and operations to build trusted relationships and unblock issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with sales and business development to source net-new sites that meet partner needs, scoping deal terms and acquisition requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work hand-in-hand with operations leaders and on-the-ground teams to ensure partners receive necessary support at launch and through ongoing operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track deployment KPIs and partner-level performance to build reporting and analyses that quantify business impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Surface partner feedback and on-the-ground learnings to shape the broader Future Mobility roadmap and product strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What we&#39;re looking for&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of relevant experience in mobility operations or business development at a fast-paced tech startup&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in future mobility including AV, drones, or eVTOL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possess well-versed knowledge in at least one of parking, mobility, or real estate&lt;/li&gt;
